## Local Development

### Prerequisites
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Python 3.12+
- Terraform >= 1.5 (for AWS resource provisioning)
- LocalStack running (`docker compose up localstack -d` from the repo root)

### Run locally

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start the service
python src/main.py

# Health check
curl http://localhost:{{SERVICE_PORT}}/health
```

### Run with Docker

```bash
docker build -t {{SERVICE_NAME}} .
docker run -p {{SERVICE_PORT}}:{{SERVICE_PORT}} {{SERVICE_NAME}}
```

