## AWS Resources (via LocalStack)

This service provisions the following resources through Terraform:

| Resource | Name | Purpose |
|----------|------|---------|
| S3 Bucket | `{{SERVICE_NAME}}-artifacts` | Artifact and file storage |
| SSM Parameter | `/local/{{SERVICE_NAME}}/config` | Runtime configuration |

### Provision resources

```bash
cd terraform
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply -auto-approve
```

### Verify on LocalStack

```bash
# List buckets
aws --endpoint-url=http://localhost:4566 s3 ls

# Read SSM config
aws --endpoint-url=http://localhost:4566 ssm get-parameter \
  --name "/local/{{SERVICE_NAME}}/config" --query Parameter.Value
```

